<item>
            <title>[SYNAPSE-698] NPE in SynapseConfiguration.destroy()</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SYNAPSE-698</link>
                <project id="12310201" key="SYNAPSE">Synapse</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;If for some reason org.apache.synapse.config.SynapseConfiguration.destroy() is called twice, a NPE results on line 767 since the synapseTimer variable has already been set to NULL.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12476668">SYNAPSE-698</key>
            <summary>NPE in SynapseConfiguration.destroy()</summary>
                <type id="1" iconUrl="https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/viewavatar?size=xsmall&amp;avatarId=21133&amp;avatarType=issuetype">Bug</type>
